刑、拘役或500,000元以下\r\n罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e8%a8%b4%2c150%2c20220825%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交訴,150,20220825,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交訴","JNO":"150","JDATE":"20220825","JTITLE":"過失致死"}